Package: turtlearena
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, turtlearena-data (>= 0.2)
Description: 3D third-person arena combat game
 Turtle Arena is an open-source Ninja Turtle fangame based on ioquake3. It
 is licensed under the GPL. It is a free stand-alone game.
 .
 This package installs the Turtle Arena client.

Package: turtlearena-server
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, turtlearena-data (>= 0.2)
Description: game server for the game Turtle Arena
 Turtle Arena is an open-source Ninja Turtle fangame based on ioquake3. It
 is licensed under the GPL. It is a free stand-alone game.
 .
 This package installs the Turtle Arena dedicated server.
